## Example Test Cases

### Negative Upload Validation (Medium priority)

```
#: 15
Priority: Medium
Case Title: (blank – same section as TC 14)
PIC: Vendor
Steps:
  1. Prepare file with 数字编号 = 1, 2, 4 (gap at 3)
  2. Attempt upload in 3PL Portal → Bid compliance procedure → Technical Bid
Expected results:
  * Upload blocked
  * Error: "Serial Number input error, continuous positive integers are required"
Pass/Fail/Skip: (blank)
Remarks: Gap in sequence rejected
```

### Core Functional Flow (High priority)

```
#: 19
Priority: High
Case Title: (blank – same section as TC 18)
PIC: Vendor
Steps:
  1. Upload 3 solutions for the same Request ID from same vendor (数字编号 1, 2, 3)
  2. Check SLS admin → Solution Management → Technical Bid Solution
Expected results:
  * System allows multiple solutions per vendor per request
  * All 3 solutions visible in SLS admin
Pass/Fail/Skip: (blank)
Remarks: 1:N relationship confirmed
```

