## Generation Workflow

```
0. Request the PRD/BRD file from the user before doing anything else.
   Do not proceed until the spec has been provided.
1. Read the PRD/spec thoroughly
2. Ask elicitation questions (sheet structure is MANDATORY — never assume)
3. Offer to preview the most complex section first
4. Incorporate user feedback on preview
5. Build full .xlsx with all sections
6. Deliver the output file
```
